name: Invesco ESG Global Bond ETF
longDescription: IWBE seeks to generate income and capital appreciation over the long-term. This Invesco ETF invests, directly or indirectly, primarily in investment-grade debt securities of governments, corporations and other issuers around the world while integrating environmental, social and governance (ESG) criteria as part of the fundamental evaluation of investment opportunities.
